Name: 2021/22 Upper Deck MVP NHL Hockey BLASTER box (15 pks/bx)
desc:
Each sealed box contains 15 packs of 6 cards.
*Your 2021-22 hockey card collection starts here with an impressive Base Set consisting of 200 regular cards and 50 High Series Star & Rookie SP cards! Collect two parallels: the popular Silver Script parallel and the all-new Ice Battles parallel!
*The Ice Battles parallel is a card-back variation set.
*The standard bio and stats are replaced with five categories with which you can play your own Pack Wars game with family, friends and fellow collectors: Overall, Speed, Strength, Skill and Awareness.
*NEW! Collect three exciting new insert sets:
*Hart Attack: This set features Hart Trophy (league MVP) contenders.
*Before and After: Each card in this uniquely-themed set, which includes many of the league’s star players, features two contrasting photos: one showing the player in his pregame attire, and another showing him in action on the ice.
*Mascot Gaming Cards: An intriguing set featuring all 30 NHL mascots! Collect the regular and Patterned Foilboard parallel versions of each.
*This year’s 20th Anniversary set pays homage to the 2001-02 “MVP Watch” design.
*Look for 2021-22 rookie cards, including divisionally-themed Rookie Redemption cards and the super rare 2021 NHL #1 Draft Pick SP Redemption cards.

Sealed Sticker Box. 50 sticker packs with 5 stickers per pack (250 Total) PANINI RTWC 2022 is the official Soccer collection for the 2022 FIFA World Cup Qatar Qualifying. This collection includes top national teams from around the globe hoping to qualify to 2022 FIFA World Cup. Showcasing the World’s best soccer players with their National Teams: * McKennie (USA) * Pulisic (USA), * Ricardo Pepi (USA) * Weah (USA) * Messi (Argentina), * Ronaldo (Portugal), * Neymar (Brasil), * Chicharito (Mexico), * Neuer (Alemania), * Pedri (Spain), * Donnarumma (Italy) * James Rodriguez (Colombia), * Alexis Sanchez (Chile), * Mbappe (France), * Griezman (France) * Bale, and so many more! Insert these stickers into your Panini 2022 FIFA World Cup Qatar Album. Look for the number on the back of the sticker and match it to the number inside the album More teams and clubs to collect! Collecting Panini Stickers is fun for the entire family! Trade your duplicate stickers with friends, then race to see who can complete the album first!

Name: 2021 Panini NBA Illusions Basketball Trading Card Blaster Box
desc: Panini presents the 2020-2021 NBA Illusions blaster box! Inside this box you will find 6 foil packs with 6 cards per pack. Look for blaster exclusive emerald and ruby parallels! Also be on the look out for retail exclusive starlight parallels! You may also find autographs in rookie signs & trophy collection signatures!
